    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "CXR\nUpright - Fluid collections >200-300cc can usually be seen\nSupine - Fluid collections >1000cc can be missed\nMainstem bronchus intubation can appear like a hemothorax on CXR\nUS\nCT is gold standard",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": [
